OL,3,CQuarter of motorists affected by
OL,4,Cbright headlights have cut night
OL,5,Cdriving
OL,7,FThree out of five respondents who
OL,8,Fsuffer from headlight glare say the
OL,9,Fproblem has worsened in the previous
OL,10,F12 months, as ITV News Midlands
OL,11,FCorrespondent Stacey Foster reports.
OL,13,FA quarter (25%) of drivers who find
OL,14,Fvehicle headlights too bright are
OL,15,Fdriving less at night because of the
OL,16,Fissue, a new survey suggests.
