OL,3,CQuarter of motorists affected by
OL,4,Cbright headlights have cut night
OL,5,Cdriving
OL,7,FThe poll of 1,866 drivers,
OL,8,Fcommissioned by the car insurance
OL,9,Fcompany RAC in December 2024,
OL,10,Findicated that 22% of participants
OL,11,Ftried to reduce their night driving.
OL,13,FNearly all drivers surveyed believe
OL,14,Fheadlights can be too bright, and 61%
OL,15,Fof those affected by glare say the
OL,16,Fproblem has become worse in the past
OL,17,Fyear, while 26% disagree.
