OL,7,FDepartment for Transport (DfT) figures
OL,8,Fshow that since 2013, bright
OL,9,Fheadlights have been a contributory
OL,10,Ffactor in an average of 280 crashes
OL,11,Fevery year on Britain's roads,
OL,12,Fincluding six fatal accidents annually.
OL,14,FA DfT spokesperson said: "We know
OL,15,Fthere is increased public concern
OL,16,Fabout headlamp glare ` that's why we
OL,17,Fhave commissioned independent research
OL,18,Fto better understand the root causes,
OL,19,Fwhich will help identify potential
OL,20,Fmitigations.
