OL,3,CQuarter of motorists affected by
OL,4,Cbright headlights have cut night
OL,5,Cdriving
OL,7,F"What has gone from a mere frustration
OL,8,Fis now having a profound impact on
OL,9,Fpeople ` whether that's momentarily
OL,10,Fbeing blinded while driving or
OL,11,Fstruggling to judge the speed or
OL,12,Fposition of a vehicle ahead.
OL,14,F"The fact such a high proportion of
OL,15,Fpeople are also driving less at night
OL,16,F` or wish they could ` is remarkable
OL,17,Fand demonstrates the need for glare to
OL,18,Fbe tackled."
