OL,12,FWhy is this happening?
OL,14,FThe RAC says modern car headlights
OL,15,Fappear brighter due to the use of bi-
OL,16,Fxenon and LED bulbs, creating a more
OL,17,Fintense beam than traditional halogen
OL,18,Flights.
