OL,7,FWhile this improves visibility for
OL,8,Fdrivers, it can make the road harder
OL,9,Fto see for others.
OL,11,FOther potential factors include badly
OL,12,Faligned headlights and the prevalence
OL,13,Fof SUVs, which generally have
OL,14,Fheadlights in a higher position.
